{"word":"H2459 - חֶלֶב - cheleb - kheh'-leb - [idiom] best","slug":"H2459","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חֶלֶב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>cheleb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kheh'-leb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] best"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D7;&#x05DC;&#x05D1;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D7;&#x05DC;&#x05D1; - cheleb  che&#x0302;leb</b> - <i>kheh'-leb, khay'-leb</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>be fat</i>; <i>fat</i>, whether literally or figuratively; hence the <i>richest</i> or <i>choice part</i>: -  X best, fat (-ness), X finest, grease, marrow."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2460\">H2460</a>, <a href=\"#/H2462\">H2462</a>, <a href=\"#/H2463\">H2463</a>, <a href=\"#/H2464\">H2464</a>, <a href=\"#/H303\">H303</a>"}]}